.org/abhisit1"><img alt='''' src=''https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0ef4352f42112e774dd50de255ace5fc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g'' srcset=''https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0ef4352f42112e774dd50de255ace5fc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x'' class=''avatar avatar-16 photo'' height=''16'' width=''16'' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/abhisit1" class="reviewer-name">abhisit1</a> el <span class="review-date">November 26, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">It helps to create and maintain all my events list properly.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Always trouble</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/marcusjott"><img alt='''' src=''https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/457451ad6a94fe71ab9188ffbf322a21?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g'' srcset=''https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/457451ad6a94fe71ab9188ffbf322a21?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x'' class=''avatar avatar-16 photo'' height=''16'' width=''16'' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/marcusjott" class="reviewer-name">marcusjott</a> el <span class="review-date">November 21, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Every single update caused trouble.\nMostly its due to a foobared layout , sometimes the switches between month / list do not work at all and others.\nIts painful since i always ha